4.1 Roles and Responsibilities

  • Role-Based Access Control

    • Currently 8 Roles:

      • System Admin

      • School Admin

      • Subject Panel Head (Renamed from Subject Panel Head)

      • Subject Form Coordinator

      • Subject Teacher

      • Principals (also Subject Panel Head of all subjects)

      • Students

      • Parent

  • System Admin can create additional Roles and assign corresponding ca= pabilities

  • The capabilities of each role are shown below

  • Remaining Capabilities of the system to be defined later

  • Need a special capability to access teacher and student accounts. On= ly Principal / School Admin / System Admin can have this capability
